{"tid":2185543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被指襲擊持警棍休班警 美籍銀行家申請控方披露《警察通例》被拒","createTime":"2020-09-02T10:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:39:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4b65590d02da4ba60f5706072ba6c2e8206290","tid":2185543,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/AKZFLRCXOZA3FHQSNMSAZI66BU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2FAKZFLRCXOZA3FHQSNMSAZI66BU%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=ed2b77d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200902%2FAKZFLRCXOZA3FHQSNMSAZI66BU%2F&h=077f2b13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200902/AKZFLRCXOZA3FHQSNMSAZI66BU/</a><br />\n<br />\n35歲美籍銀行家涉於去年12月在港鐵銅鑼灣站襲擊追截別人的休班警，被控襲警等罪。由於休班警當日曾使用警棍，銀行家要求控方披露《警察通例》對使用武力的指引。裁判官林希維早前聽罷陳詞後，今作出裁決，指辯方要求披露的資料與刑事審訊無關，即使警員違反指引，亦將面對內部紀律聆訊，拒絕辯方申請。案件押後至本月18日聽取被告答辯。"},{"pid":"3b8cdb8767a64ed14f78f3c6946869986e42d621","tid":2185543,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0157efd052a7d3f3b432ab9a84918029f23a9e4b","tid":2185543,"uid":189564,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"行政主導 三權合作成功例子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3e2884a84a4c68592aea979a6190eb5c57fd7c","tid":2185543,"uid":183685,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020